{"type":"article","id":7341,"title":"浙江小学生当小白鼠被“上环”，被实时监测上课是否走神","uid":9304,"topics":[],"contents":"头戴的铁环是一种脑机接口头环，可检测脑电波，给学生上课和写作业时的注意力集中情况打分，实时传输到老师电脑上，并像考试排名一样发到家长群里。注意力分数被评估出来。<br>\n然而，有学生说带上会痛，带上之后感觉有个印紧紧的压在头上。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EIIrTiWUwAE4OAG?format=jpg&amp;name=360x360\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EIIrTiWUwAE4OAG?format=jpg&amp;name=360x360\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EIIrTiWUwAE4OAG?format=jpg&amp;name=360x360\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EIIrWgwUwAATw9e?format=jpg&amp;name=360x360\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EIIrWgwUwAATw9e?format=jpg&amp;name=360x360\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EIIrWgwUwAATw9e?format=jpg&amp;name=360x360\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EIIrXK2U8AEYPX1?format=jpg&amp;name=360x360\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EIIrXK2U8AEYPX1?format=jpg&amp;name=360x360\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EIIrXK2U8AEYPX1?format=jpg&amp;name=360x360\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EIIrT89VUAAQ4o9?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EIIrT89VUAAQ4o9?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EIIrT89VUAAQ4o9?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-10-31","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":0}